Air Tool Lubricant, Winter Grade, 55 Gallon Drum

Air tools are an investment; protect them with high quality Air Tool Lubricant. Coilhose Air Tool Lubricant is specially formulated ISO 22 lubricant, designed to prolong the life of air tools and accessories.

Available in Standard or Wintergrade, Air Tool Lubricant can keep your operation running all year.

  • Made in USA
    • Inhibits the Formation of Rust
  • Non-Detergent, Non-Corrosive, Non-Reactive, and Stable
  • Removes Moisture
  • Temperature Range
    		• -45°F +
    Product Information
    DescriptionAir Tool Lubricant, Winter Grade, 55 Gallon Drum
    PackagingDrum
